    <string name="setup_adb_guide">To grant this permission, connect your tablet to a Windows PC via USB and run an ADB command.\n\nStep-by-step instructions:\n\n1. Download \"SDK Platform-Tools\" from:\nhttps://developer.android.com/studio/releases/platform-tools\n\n2. Extract the downloaded ZIP file\n\n3. On your tablet, enable Developer Options:\nSettings ‚Üí About tablet ‚Üí Tap \"Build number\" 7 times\n\n4. Enable USB debugging:\nSettings ‚Üí Developer options ‚Üí USB debugging ‚Üí ON\n\n5. Connect your tablet to the PC via USB cable\n\n6. Open PowerShell as Administrator on your PC, navigate to the platform-tools folder, then run:</string>
    <string name="setup_adb_command">adb shell pm grant com.minsoo.ultranavbar android.permission.WRITE_SECURE_SETTINGS</string>
